[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.   

You <b>COULD</b> make a game-forcing cuebid here, but a much better description of your hand is a leap to 4\H, the spot where you know you want to play. If partner has any extra strength he will know to bid again. In this case he has a bare minimum and passes.

Notice that if you had made a cuebid, partner would probably end up playing 4\H and the opening \S lead would be right through your \SK.}

